metadata.name: Truckz
metadata.description:
"BETTER UTILITY THAN A TRUCK WITH MORE PERFORMANCE THAN A SPORTS CAR."

"Truckz" is my slides remake, with tesla truck as the concept. 

My favourite part of this design is tread like soles. 
All designs are custom made on blender. Some may be recreated into wearables. 

Thanks for supporting my journey.
